# Implementation Plan - Phase 6: Advanced AI Lead Scoring

This phase implements the "Lead Intelligence Engine," a core value proposition of Agencia B2B. It leverages Generative AI to analyze gathered lead data, classify opportunities, and provide tactical outreach recommendations.

## Proposed Changes

### [Backend] Lead Intelligence Engine

#### [NEW] [intelligence-service.ts](file:///c:/Users/fmonf/Desktop/Software%20Enginnering%20LAPTOP/Agencia%20B2B/agencia-web-b2b/src/lib/leads/intelligence-service.ts)
*   Implement `LeadIntelligenceService` class.
*   Function `analyzeLead(leadId: string)`:
    *   Fetch Lead data (including scraper results).
    *   Call OpenAI with a specialized prompt to analyze "Digital Gaps" based on category and metadata.
    *   Map AI output to the `LeadIntelligence` schema.
    *   Store results in the database.
*   Function `generateOutreachCopy(leadId: string)`:
    *   Use AI to craft a personalized WhatsApp and Email template based on the `topProblem` identified during analysis.

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///c:/Users/fmonf/Desktop/Software%20Enginnering%20LAPTOP/Agencia%20B2B/agencia-web-b2b/src/app/api/leads/%5Bid%5D/intelligence/route.ts)
*   Create POST endpoint to trigger AI analysis for a specific lead.
*   Create GET endpoint to retrieve the latest intelligence data.

### [Frontend] UI Integration

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/fmonf/Desktop/Software%20Enginnering%20LAPTOP/Agencia%20B2B/agencia-web-b2b/src/app/%5Blocale%5D/admin/leads/page.tsx)
*   Add a "Hot/Cold" badge column to the lead table.
*   Display `opportunityScore` as a progress bar or colored indicator.

#### [NEW] [LeadIntelligenceCard.tsx](file:///c:/Users/fmonf/Desktop/Software%20Enginnering%20LAPTOP/Agencia%20B2B/agencia-web-b2b/src/components/leads/LeadIntelligenceCard.tsx)
*   A premium UI component to display:
    *   Lead Tier (HOT/WARM/COLD) with vibrant colors.
    *   Digital Gap breakdown (SSL, Chatbot, Performance).
    *   Top Problem & Revenue Opportunity.
    *   One-click copy buttons for AI-generated messages.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
*   `vitest` for `LeadIntelligenceService`: Mock OpenAI responses and verify correct mapping to Prisma models.
*   Playwright test to verify that clicking "Analyze AI" updates the lead details with intelligent insights.

### Manual Verification
*   Trigger analysis on a seeded lead and verify that the generated WhatsApp message sounds professional and contextual.
*   Verify UI responsiveness on mobile views for the new Intelligence Card.
